    <Placemark>
      <name>Note:</name>
      <description><![CDATA[There is no perfect neighborhood map of this type with hard borders because it is subjective. We have tried to make the best map possible by taking many opinions and all the sources available into account, but there will always be disagreements. Here are the borders we are least confident in:                                                                                                                                  <br> South Richmond Hill/South Ozone Park (Liberty ave, 109th ave or Linden Blvd)                                        Financial District and Tribeca<br>Downtown Brooklyn/Boerum Hill (Schermerhorn or Atlantic)                                 Midwood/Sheepshead Bay<br>South Richmond Hill/Ozone park                                Is Van Cortlandt Village Real?      <br>Jamaica/St. Albans                                          Astoria/Woodside                                                  Little Yemen sub-neighborhood of Van Nest or Morris Park<br>Concourse northern border<br>City Line real/ correct borders?<br>Auburndale/Fresh Meadows<br>Bay Ridge/Dyker Heights (southern section) Gravesend northern border<br>Marine park/Sheepshead Bay                                        <br>                                                                                            The white areas are places larger than a block where the public access is restricted.<br>If you have opinions please contact @samlernerdreamer instgram                                     ]]></description>
      <styleUrl>#line-000000-1200</styleUrl>
      <LineString>
        <tessellate>1</tessellate>
        <coordinates>
          34.4688863,31.4994345,0
          34.4689785,31.4994034,0
        </coordinates>
      </LineString>
    </Placemark>
